SUMMARY:Pilgrim Prayers Weekly Team Standup
DESCRIPTION:Weekly team coordination and performance review
 MEETING DETAILS:
 - Led by: Agency Manager (Gatekeeper Agent)
 - Attendees: All agents + Project Lead
 - Duration: 90 minutes

 AGENDA:
 1. Performance Review (20 min) - Last week's metrics and insights
 2. Status Check (15 min) - Current week deliverable progress
 3. Strategic Recommendations (20 min) - What to focus on next week
 4. Action Planning (30-40 min) - Assign next week's tasks to all agents
 5. Priority Summary (5 min) - Clear priority for each agent

 OUTCOMES:
 ✅ Clear task assignments for all agents
 ✅ Performance data drives all decisions
 ✅ Competitive intelligence updates
 ✅ Monday EOD deadline status confirmed
 ✅ New opportunities identified

 PREPARATION:
 Agency Manager prepares metrics dashboard and recommendations on Friday/Saturday

 DOCUMENTATION:
 - Meeting minutes saved to project
 - Decisions logged to M-memory files
 - Task assignments shared immediately after

